title: Jeff Johnson Interview and more
itunes:title: Jeff Johnson Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had Jeff Johnson from Bet show Man Cave stop by, where he spoke about the concept of the show and accidentally found some stuff out about Charlamagne. Moreover after devastating news about a Florida school shooting Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the gun man of the shooting Nikolas Cruz. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
